## Pokémon FireRed/LeafGreen Alt Main Raichu

Before starting your run, make sure your save file has the following:
  - Text: Fast
  - Battle Animations: Off
  - Style: SHIFT
  - Button Mode: L=A

Give yourself a 1 character name  
Optional: Get the PC potion  
Head outside then, head north towards the grass have Oak stop you  
Mash through text until you can pick Squirtle (middle Pokeball). Give it a one character name

Head down and fight your rival

:::::trainer[Rival 1]
  Tackle spam (TW once if you did very little damage)
:::::

Put cursor on Bag when leaving lab (skips a cutscene before Route 1)

Grab the Potion from mart guy

Do not kill any wild pokes on Route 1

Grab the parcel at the mart then head back to Oak’s lab

Catch Rattata/Pidgey if you come across them on the second way up (Tackle to weaken)
  - Catch at least one HM friend here

Head to Viridian Forest

- Skip all the Bugcatchers until Sammy
- Grab the Antidote after the second Bugcatcher (after the sign)
- Grab the Potion in the corner before Sammy
- Grab the hidden Potion next to Sammy
- Stall for Pika before Sammy: Tackle a lvl 3 once (Thundershock does 6-(8)), yoloball a lvl 5 (Thundershock usually does 10-(12))
- Switch Pika to the front

Note: If male Pika has -Def Nature and low Def IV, you will not make it past Viridian Gym.

:::::::trainer[Bug Catcher Sammy]
  :::::pokemon[Weedle]
    - Swap to Squirtle, Tail Whip once, then Tackle spam
    - Weedle's Poison Sting always does 3
	- A poison tick does 2 (at lvl 6)
  :::::
:::::::

If you got poisoned, Antidote immediately after the fight:  
Head to the gym, fight the minion

:::::::trainer[Camper Liam]
  :::::pokemon[Geodude]
    Switch to Squirtle and Bubble x2
  :::::
  :::::pokemon[Sandshrew]
    Switch to Pika, back to Squirtle, and Bubble x3-4
  :::::
:::::::

:::::::trainer[Leader Brock]
  :::::pokemon[Geodude]
    Switch to Squirtle and Bubble twice  
    Watch Squirtle's Defense on the level up
  :::::
  :::::pokemon[Onix]
    Switch to Pika, then to an HM friend, (potion Squirtle,) then switch in Squirtle and Bubble x2  
    Rock Tomb does 11-(13) with 16-17 Def, 10-(12) with 18-19 Def, and 8-(10) with 20+ Def.
  :::::
:::::::

Switch setting to Set mode
After leaving the gym, enter the Mart

:::card
Sell: Rock Tomb

Buy:
- 11 Potions
- 4 Antidotes
- 3 Awakenings
- 4 Repels
:::

Head to Route 3 to get your running shoes

