Avoid the lass

If you didn’t catch a Flyer yet, catch a Spearow/Pidgey now in the grass below the lass (QA to weaken)

Grab the hidden Persim Berry to the left of the poke center
Heal in the center
Enter Mt. Moon

Mt. Moon menu:
  - Register the TM case
  - Give the Persim Berry to Pika
  - Use a Repel (can still get encounters on B2F, do NOT try to catch Paras)

Grab the Rare Candy below the Bug Catcher and the escape rope  
Get the hidden Ether and TM Thief (down the ladder near Youngster Josh)  
Get the Revive  
Dodge the Rocket spinner

